summary: Simple conversion of Elewin Pumps UNP by elewin to use NiOverride by ousnius.
descriptionHtml:
Another conversion this time of the very popular [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29687/?tab=logs]Elewin Pumps - High Heels For UNP[/url]﻿ by none other than [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/5807238]elewin[/url]
All credits go to her. 

What has been done with the original mod:

1.Removed the HDT dependancy
2.Added the script provided from [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/4291759]ousnius[/url] using NIFskope
3.Repacked and uploaded

The original mod can be found here:  [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29687/?tab=logs]Elewin Pumps - High Heels For UNP[/url]

My other Conversions:

1.Elewin Pumps 2 NiOverride High Heels Conversion : [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/92702]here[/url]
2.Sotteta Huntress Armor 2k UNP NiOVerride Conversion: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/92714]here[/url]﻿
3.Gwelda Red RIding Hood UNP 2k NIoverride: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/92740]here[/url]
